{"tid":2102472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不清楚就不要瞎掰！其實祖國內地的發展已經改善了很多","createTime":"2020-07-10T13:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T16:44:46.000Z","uid":52658,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"13454e4a266f41b721be9aad52c6694c9420409a","tid":2102472,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:13:43.000Z","msg":"祖國地大物博<br />\n<br />\n但看大多數香港人只會去過台北 新北還有台中拉~<br />\n我必須說明一下<br />\n我們內地其實沒你們想像得那麼鄉下拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次到了南投縣旅遊<br />\n市區其實就跟台北市差別不大膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n草屯夜市根本有資格跟士林夜市定孤支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出了市區還可以騎機車到仁愛鄉泡溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網絡上經常看到蠻多的屁孩可撥仔黑我們南投內地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好膽就過來旅遊一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90aaf177d9cc5909e46838dcb69b1e86135642f","tid":2102472,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:15:10.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n等疫情之後啦"},{"pid":"90cc12f1da3cb837bf311b90b51ff52ffcdb8b96","tid":2102472,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:16:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>聽日後日去投票</strong></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\"><strong>聽日後日去投票</strong></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>聽日後日去投票</strong></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">聽日後日去投票</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\">聽日後日去投票</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"navy\">聽日後日去投票</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"purple\">聽日後日去投票</span></span></strong>"},{"pi